铜蛇形器的歧羽纹、臣字目，其中臣字目纹样也广泛出现在中原地区的青铜器和玉器上，彰显着中华文明多元一体、兼收并蓄。吉祥物身上由景泰蓝工艺刻画背部缠枝纹，寓意“生生不息”，由花丝镶嵌工艺勾勒出海棠、玉兰、桃花与牡丹，寓意“春回大地”。 蓬勃生机染青绿 叠翠流金共迎春 “巳升升”以青绿色为主调，象征春意盎然、蓬勃生机，配色取自鹦哥绿、品绿、吐绶蓝、青金石、荷花白、柑黄、龙膏烛等中国传统色彩。 伴随着“巳升升”的亮相，总台《2025年春节联欢晚会》的脚步也越来越近。“巳升升”邀您一起相约春晚，共同迎接欢乐吉祥、喜气洋洋的乙巳蛇年。 https://content-static.cctvnews.cctv.com/snow-book/index.html?item_id=3354845075277017508"},"attached_info":"CkAI3MOK9e637eR7EAMaCTExMjEyMzQ3NSDJwrW6BjAAOCxACnIKNTczNDM3MjUxMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-234af9182200f4418bcbc28e5508657a_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1733289652.859440","card_id":"Q_653864144","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":653864144,"title":"西幻世界精灵的农业会是怎么样的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653864144","type":"question","created":1713864558,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":95,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5456,15285,48860],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I3MOK9e637eR7EAMaCTEwNzU4MDgwNiDu/p2xBjAAOF9AC3IJNjUzODY0MTQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2e141e61f6aa64fe431cf06a81d2e12d_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1733289652.859710","card_id":"Q_5872043001","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":5872043001,"title":"为何普通人大多都是为了生存忙活了一生?","url":"https://api.zhihu